ime":"2024-06-19T21:47:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224399886\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022224768\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221718832873\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022146349\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DDE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, DDE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nParadox - who I\u0027d imagine had money to burn - have just killed their Sims competitor, \u003Cem\u003ELife by You\u003C/em\u003E, which theoretically could have been the cash grab of the decade if it outran Sims 5, which it would likely have.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m still scratching my head over this one. They also shutdown the Studio, as this was their only project - what also means that they didn\u0027t had the faintest idea on what to do with them after the launch, what also means that they would probably shut them down anyway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m sincerely flabbergasted.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-20T00:01:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m guessing there\u0027s more to that story than \u0022hey let\u0027s close this studio for no reason.\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lisias","CreatedById":187168,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-06-20T06:08:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224399904\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022224768\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data